      • onCameraFragmentImageDetected

        void onCameraFragmentImageDetected(java.lang.String productInfo)
        Called when 2D products are found
        Parameters:
        productInfo - representing a short info about the matched 2D products. Can be empty in case no match has been found.

        This method will be called upon a successful match either from a live video preview (automatic scanner) or from an image captured (by pressing snap button) or picked from the gallery
